original_title: The Woodsmaster Volume 02 Survival Shelter Selection
overview: Learn the survival priorities and how to meet them! What is the rule of threes? You learn the heat loss mechanisms, site selection, pine log shelters, the Firebed, and more incredible Woodsmaster Tips, Lore and Techniques. This tape is a stunner!
title: The Woodsmaster Volume 02 Survival Shelter Selection
